headline: Digital Realty Trust (DLR): Strong Growth Outlook, Strategic Expansion, and Positive Analyst Sentiment Fuel REIT Potential
summary: Digital Realty Trust, Inc. (NYSE:DLR) is one of Goldman Sachs’ top REIT stock picks. On January 29, analysts at KeyBanc reiterated a Sector Weight rating on Digital Realty Trust, Inc. (NYSE:DLR). According to the research firm, the company’s risk/reward balance appears neutral. KeyBanc expects the company to deliver revenue growth of 10% plus in 2026, […]

headline: 36 U.S. REITs Expected To Raise Dividends In Q1 2026
summary: 36 publicly traded US REITs are projected to increase dividend payouts in the first quarter, according to S&P Global Market Intelligence forecasts.
